      "description": "Home testing using 3x3_HAMMING63 markers (HD=3, much more reliable). Official marker images: https://github.com/nicolocarpignoli/artoolkit-barcode-markers-collection/tree/master/3x3_hamming_6_3 — place marker 0 flat on the floor as the origin, tape markers 1 and 2 to walls or props at measured distances.",
